name: Nintendo Switch Online: Game Boy Advance
overview: Advance your play with Game Boy Advance – Nintendo Switch Online. With a Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack membership, access a collection of classic and colorful Game Boy™ Advance games to play anytime, anywhere! Shrink down for a big adventure in The Legend of Zelda™: The Minish Cap and master sibling strategies in Mario & Luigi™: Superstar Saga.
